---
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../../../components/Header.astro";
---

<Layout title="Grabaciones de Sesiones | SIMG">
  <Header slot="header" />
  <main>
    <h1>Grabaciones de Sesiones</h1>

    <section class="intro-section">
      <p>
        Accede a las grabaciones de nuestras sesiones anteriores para ponerte al
        día con el contenido perdido o repasar temas importantes. Nuestras
        sesiones están disponibles en nuestro canal de YouTube para todos los
        interesados en modelos generativos y temas de IA.
      </p>
      <div class="youtube-channel-link">
        <a
          href="https://www.youtube.com/@simg-UN"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="24"
            height="24"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="#ff0000"
            ><path
              d="M19.615 3.184c-3.604-.246-11.631-.245-15.23 0-3.897.266-4.356 2.62-4.385 8.816.029 6.185.484 8.549 4.385 8.816 3.6.245 11.626.246 15.23 0 3.897-.266 4.356-2.62 4.385-8.816-.029-6.185-.484-8.549-4.385-8.816zm-10.615 12.816v-8l8 3.993-8 4.007z"
            ></path></svg
          >
          Visita nuestro Canal de YouTube
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="recordings-section">
      <h2>Grabaciones Recientes</h2>

      <div class="recording-card">
        <div class="recording-info">
          <h3>Mecanismos de Atención en Modelos de Lenguaje Grandes</h3>
          <p class="date">25 de agosto, 2025</p>
          <p class="description">
            Esta sesión explora los mecanismos de atención avanzados utilizados
            en los modelos de lenguaje más grandes de la actualidad. Discutimos
            atención multi-cabeza, atención cruzada y cómo estos mecanismos
            permiten a los modelos procesar contextos largos de manera
            eficiente.
          </p>
          <div class="tags">
            <span>LLMs</span>
            <span>Atención</span>
            <span>Transformers</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="recording-link">
          <a
            href="https://www.youtube.com/@simg-UN"
            class="watch-button"
            target="_blank">Ver en YouTube</a
          >
          <p class="duration">Duración: 1:42:15</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="recording-card">
        <div class="recording-info">
          <h3>Embeddings Avanzados para Aplicaciones Multimodales</h3>
          <p class="date">18 de agosto, 2025</p>
          <p class="description">
            Un análisis profundo de embeddings multimodales, explorando cómo
            representar imágenes, texto y audio en espacios vectoriales
            unificados. Demostramos aplicaciones prácticas usando modelos de
            código abierto.
          </p>
          <div class="tags">
            <span>Embeddings</span>
            <span>Multimodal</span>
            <span>Espacios Vectoriales</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="recording-link">
          <a
            href="https://www.youtube.com/@simg-UN"
            class="watch-button"
            target="_blank">Ver en YouTube</a
          >
          <p class="duration">Duración: 1:56:30</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="recording-card">
        <div class="recording-info">
          <h3>Construyendo Sistemas RAG Eficientes con Técnicas Modernas</h3>
          <p class="date">11 de agosto, 2025</p>
          <p class="description">
            Aprende a construir sistemas de Generación Aumentada por
            Recuperación que combinan el poder de bases de conocimiento con
            modelos generativos. Cubrimos técnicas como búsqueda híbrida,
            optimización de fragmentos y compresión de contexto.
          </p>
          <div class="tags">
            <span>RAG</span>
            <span>Recuperación de Conocimiento</span>
            <span>Búsqueda Vectorial</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="recording-link">
          <a
            href="https://www.youtube.com/@simg-UN"
            class="watch-button"
            target="_blank">Ver en YouTube</a
          >
          <p class="duration">Duración: 1:49:20</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="more-videos">
        <a
          href="https://www.youtube.com/@simg-UN"
          class="more-videos-link"
          target="_blank"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="20"
            height="20"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="currentColor"
            class="more-icon"
            ><path
              d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm6 13h-5v5h-2v-5h-5v-2h5v-5h2v5h5v2z"
            ></path></svg
          >
          Ver más videos en nuestro canal de YouTube
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="archive-section">
      <h2>Archivo</h2>
      <p>
        ¿Buscando grabaciones más antiguas? Consulta nuestro archivo completo
        organizado por semestres.
      </p>

      <div class="archive-links">
        <a href="#" class="archive-link">Sesiones 2023-1</a>
        <a href="#" class="archive-link">Sesiones 2022-2</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="access-info">
      <h2>Suscríbete a Nuestro Canal</h2>
      <p>
        ¡No te pierdas ninguno de nuestros próximos contenidos! Suscríbete a
        nuestro canal de YouTube para recibir notificaciones sobre nuevos
        videos, sesiones en vivo y contenido educativo sobre modelos generativos
        e investigación en IA.
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://www.youtube.com/@simg-UN"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="access-button">Suscríbete Ahora</a
      >
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    padding: 2rem;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-family: "Arial", sans-serif;
    color: #333;
  }

  h1 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    color: #2c3e50;
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    padding-bottom: 15px;
  }

  h1::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 25%;
    width: 50%;
    height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #3498db, #7dc8ff);
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  h2 {
    color: #2980b9;
    margin: 2.5rem 0 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.9rem;
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
    padding-bottom: 10px;
  }

  h2::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 60px;
    height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #3498db, transparent);
    border-radius: 3px;
  }

  h3 {
    color: #2c3e50;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
  }

  p {
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .intro-section {
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #f0f7ff, #e6f2ff);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    border-left: 5px solid #3498db;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .intro-section::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: -50px;
    right: -50px;
    width: 150px;
    height: 150px;
    background: radial-gradient(
      circle,
      rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.1) 0%,
      rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) 70%
    );
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .intro-section::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -30px;
    left: 20%;
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
    background: radial-gradient(
      circle,
      rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.08) 0%,
      rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) 70%
    );
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .recordings-section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .recording-card {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #ffffff, #f9faff);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    transition:
      transform 0.3s ease,
      box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-top: 4px solid #3498db;
  }

  .recording-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
  }

  .recording-card::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #3498db, #7dc8ff);
    transform: scaleX(0);
    transform-origin: left;
    transition: transform 0.5s ease;
  }

  .recording-card:hover::after {
    transform: scaleX(1);
  }

  .recording-info {
    flex: 3;
    padding-right: 1.5rem;
  }

  .recording-link {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    border-left: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .date {
    color: #7f8c8d;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .description {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .tags span {
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.2),
      rgba(125, 200, 255, 0.2)
    );
    color: #1a5fb4;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.85rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    border: 1px solid rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.3);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.1);
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .tags span:hover {
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.3),
      rgba(125, 200, 255, 0.3)
    );
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 3px 6px rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.15);
  }

  .tags span::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(
      to right,
      rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) 0%,
      rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3) 50%,
      rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) 100%
    );
    transform: translateX(-100%);
    transition: transform 0.6s;
  }

  .tags span:hover::after {
    transform: translateX(100%);
  }

  .watch-button {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3498db, #2980b9);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.3);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .watch-button::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2980b9, #1a5fb4);
    z-index: -1;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  }

  .watch-button:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.4);
  }

  .watch-button:hover::after {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .duration {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #34495e;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    background-color: rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.05);
    padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .archive-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .archive-link {
    display: inline-block;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #f0f7ff, #e6f2ff);
    color: #3498db;
    padding: 0.85rem 1.7rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border: 1px solid rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.2);
    box-shadow: 0 3px 8px rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.1);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .archive-link::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(
      to right,
      transparent,
      rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.1),
      transparent
    );
    transform: translateX(-100%);
    transition: transform 0.6s ease;
  }

  .archive-link:hover {
    background-color: #e0f2fe;
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 5px 12px rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.15);
    color: #2980b9;
  }

  .archive-link:hover::before {
    transform: translateX(100%);
  }

  .access-info {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f7ff, #e6f2ff);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-top: 4px solid #3498db;
  }

  .access-info::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: -100px;
    right: -100px;
    width: 200px;
    height: 200px;
    background: radial-gradient(
      circle,
      rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.05) 0%,
      rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) 70%
    );
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .access-button {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: #3498db;
    color: white;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: background-color 0.2s;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .access-button:hover {
    background-color: #2980b9;
  }

  .youtube-channel-link {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .youtube-channel-link a {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff0000, #cc0000);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.8rem 1.8rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .youtube-channel-link a:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.4);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #cc0000, #990000);
  }

  .youtube-channel-link svg {
    margin-right: 10px;
  }

  .more-videos {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }

  .more-videos-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    color: #3498db;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 0.8rem 1.8rem;
    border: 2px solid rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.3);
    border-radius: 50px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #f0f7ff, #e6f2ff);
    box-shadow: 0 3px 8px rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.1);
  }

  .more-videos-link:hover {
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #e6f2ff, #d4e6ff);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 5px 12px rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.15);
    color: #2980b9;
    border-color: rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.5);
  }

  .more-icon {
    margin-right: 10px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .recording-card {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .recording-link {
      border-left: none;
      border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      padding-left: 0;
      padding-top: 1.5rem;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
